<a class="title" href="/nodes/97010/comments/1422242">Effet boule de neige ?</a>
</h2>
<p class="meta">
Posté par <a href="/users/med" rel="author">med</a> <time class="updated" datetime="2013-01-08T17:47:34+01:00"><span class="date">le 08/01/13</span> <span class="time">à 17:47</span></time>.
